----------------------------------------------
Build Pipeline
----------------------------------------------

a Build Pipeline at minimum includes:
- Compiling
- Tests
- Deploy

----------------------------------------------
Trigger Build
----------------------------------------------
By default: push to master
- can be configured in settings

----------------------------------------------
Travis CI
----------------------------------------------
The only required configuration is specifying
the programming language

1. Log in to TravisCI with GitHub
2. create .travis.yml

----------------------------------------------
.travis.yml
----------------------------------------------
The only required configuration is specifying
the programming language

# Build only
(language: java)
- compiles sources
- executes tests